        <title>POSIX file systems backup driver</title>
        <paragraph>The POSIX file systems backup driver backs up volumes of any type to
            POSIX file systems.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>To enable the POSIX file systems backup driver, include the following
            option in the <literal>cinder.conf</literal> file:</paragraph>
        <literal_block highlight_args="{}" language="ini" linenos="False" xml:space="preserve">backup_driver = cinder.backup.drivers.posix</literal_block>
        <paragraph>The following configuration options are available for the POSIX
            file systems backup driver.</paragraph>
